The order of executing the playbook is according to the filename. For example 1-xxx.yml [first],2-xxx.yml[second].......

Playbook1:
Create Linux VM with vm_size specification [Standard_DS1_v2] default os_disk size of 30G
Playbook2:
Resize VM vm_size specification [Standard_DS2_v2] and os_disk_size of 64G.
